div.head: Description of changes for 2013.01
div.p: This is the first public version of this text. It is a first draft created from a copy of the descriptive transcription of the St. Victor manuscript. A transcription of the Sorbonne text still needs to be completed. A collation comparision will follow and then more corrections and additions. Troublesome transcription points have been marked as unclear. Titles and Name have been given reference aattributes to point to their canonical forms. Citations, Cross-References, and a critical apparatus still need to be constructed.
